Restart System, Once restarted use down arrow key to select the rescue/recovery partition. Press the e key on keyboard
Change Root

Type Rd.break at the end of the line seen below. Once Entered use ctrl-x key
Change Root-1

Now at bash# prompt Enter the following commands

Change Root-2

mount -o remount,rw /sysroot
chroot /sysroot
passwd root --stdin (using command you can see your pw)
redhat123
touch /.autorelabel
exit
exit


